          -  Subjects with or without a clinical diagnosis of asthma

        Exclusion criteria:

          -  Subjects with chronic cough

          -  Severe CAD

          -  MI within the last 3 months

          -  Cystic fibrosis

          -  Tuberculosis

          -  Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD)
